Core Capabilities
- Amp modeling with three configurable virtual amplifier channels per plugin.
- Cabinet simulation with impulse response loading and microphone positioning controls.
- Integrated pre-effects and post-effects, including compression, delay, reverb.
- Real-time utilities: tuner, metronome, MIDI learn, noise gate, preset browsing.
- Advanced performance features: transpose, automatic doubling, and DAW-compatible plugin formats.

